Creation of table and text table
======================================

First Domain for Iitem ID- ZDITEMID:
- /nse11
- domain- ZDITEMID, click on create
- shortdescription Iteam id
- datatype (click on on search box and choose NUMC
- no. characters give 10
- click on check syntac and activate and save it as local object
-

Second Domain for Iitem Description- ZDITEMDES:
- /nse11
- domain- ZDITEMDESC, click on create
- shortdescription IteaM Description
- datatype (click on on search box and choose CHAR
- no. characters give 40
- click on check syntac and activate and save it as local object

First Dataelement for item domain-ZDEITEMID:
- click on datatype - ZDEITEMID
- click on create
- choose dataelement
- short description - item id
- in domain give ZDITEMID
- click on field label
- give item id in all 4 blocks
- click on syntac check and click on active and click on locla object

Second Dataelement for item domain-ZDEITEMIDesc:
- click on datatype - ZDEITEMIDESC
- click on create
- choose dataelement
- short description - item description
- in domain give ZDITEMIDESC
- click on field label
- give item Desc in all 4 blocks
- click on syntac check and click on active and click on locla object

Creation of primary table:
- ose11
- databasetable ZTITEM
- click on create
- short description: item table - Primary table
- choose delivery claass - C
- Databroswer - display/maintanance Allowed
- click on fields
-  Field     key  Initi           Dataelement   
 MANDT         <                   MANDT
 ITEM ID       <                   ZDEITEMID
- click on techical settings
- Data class - choose  APPL2
- Size category- 0
- click on save 
- click on back
- click on activete and save

Creation of texttable:

-ose11
- databasetable - ZTITEMT
- click on create
- short description: Item Details- Text table
- delivery class - C
- Databrowser - Display/Maintenance Allowed
- click on fields
-  Filed     key  Initi           Dataelement   
 MANDT         <                   MANDT
 SPRAS         <                   SPRAS
 ITEM ID       <                   ZDEITEMID
 ITEMSDSC                          ZDEITEMIDESC
- Click on activate and save as local object
- Click on technical setting and choose table is language-depndenet but not traansalate
- dataclass - APPL2
- Size category -0
- click on save
- click  on activate, click on save

